{"tid":1781191,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警隊半年人均月領1.4萬元加班津貼","createTime":"2019-12-13T03:32:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T06:07:47.000Z","uid":3302,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0311e0eaa2a85daeea6d3eeefcd8f722adf6b579","tid":1781191,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T03:32:17.000Z","msg":"立法會財委會討論公務員加薪建議，政府提供文件首次披露，今年6月至11月半年間，警務處平均每月領取紀律部隊逾時工作津貼的人員約1.1萬人，總開支約9.5億元。<br />\n<br />\n按數據推算，過去半年，警員每月平均領取近1.6億元逾時工作津貼，平均每人每月領逾1.4萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2328910/警隊半年加班津貼近10億+人均月領1.4萬元\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2328910%2F%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E5%8A%A0%E7%8F%AD%E6%B4%A5%E8%B2%BC%E8%BF%9110%E5%84%84%2B%E4%BA%BA%E5%9D%87%E6%9C%88%E9%A0%981.4%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6vilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=ecc7c86b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2328910/警隊半年加班津貼近10億+人均月領1.4萬元</a>"},{"pid":"763243cb846dd3373d61cad2e5f30bfa4533d24f","tid":1781191,"uid":3302,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T03:33:25.000Z","msg":"睇到好撚嬲<br />\n市民俾錢請人打自己輪姦自己咩玩法？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>一齊罷交稅養廢人</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"97bb82b72c7bb2a9f63416ff15f09ba264238800","tid":1781191,"uid":133743,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T03:41:15.000Z","msg":"為咁少錢可以做狗<br />\n啲黑警真係cheap到..."},{"pid":"7f6ece5c5f864e1c7d65e8f58cbe5cc1ae9890ce","tid":1781191,"uid":3302,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"97bb82b72c7bb2a9f63416ff15f09ba264238800","tid":1781191,"uid":133743,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T03:41:15.000Z","msg":"為咁少錢可以做狗<br />\n啲黑警真係cheap到..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T03:43:02.000Z","msg":"1.4萬*6個月=每個人呃撚左8萬4千蚊.."},{"pid":"86c925b19c93e39b06862f25a626382481d30de8","t